WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.466 --> 00:00:01.266
Lolo

2
00:00:02.266 --> 00:00:05.500
This relationship between us was wrong

3
00:00:05.600 --> 00:00:08.000
But it hasn't caused much consequence

4
00:00:08.466 --> 00:00:11.066
So that's the end of it.

5
00:00:12.600 --> 00:00:13.900
From now on

6
00:00:14.300 --> 00:00:15.633
You are still my little tree

7
00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:18.033
I will never have any other feelings for you

8
00:00:19.600 --> 00:00:22.900
Guo Sijun, my behavior has bothered you all these years

9
00:00:22.933 --> 00:00:24.200
It affected you.

10
00:00:24.333 --> 00:00:25.600
I apologize.

11
00:00:26.666 --> 00:00:28.566
Let go of me, we haven't finished talking yet

12
00:00:28.566 --> 00:00:30.766
What do you want me to say?

13
00:00:31.200 --> 00:00:33.666
Lolo, we shouldn't have done this

14
00:00:33.666 --> 00:00:35.000
It shouldn't be like this

15
00:00:35.000 --> 00:00:37.966
Hu Sijun, then tell me what we are doing

16
00:00:37.966 --> 00:00:39.433
Are we together?

17
00:00:39.500 --> 00:00:40.300
OK

18
00:00:41.333 --> 00:00:42.566
Pardon me?

19
00:00:45.466 --> 00:00:47.900
I said we are together

20
00:00:48.133 --> 00:00:50.066
Jinlong, are you crazy?

21
00:00:50.066 --> 00:00:51.466
I wasn't kidding you.

22
00:00:51.933 --> 00:00:52.900
Guo Zijun

23
00:00:53.733 --> 00:00:55.066
In the past ten years

24
00:00:55.066 --> 00:00:57.600
You have never experienced choosing me

25
00:00:58.000 --> 00:00:59.966
Why do you regret it now?

26
00:01:00.300 --> 00:01:03.200
Forget it, I don't love you anymore

